{
  "stem": "2004.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But by the same token, we weren't starving, either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were able to secure food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, food was rather difficult to obtain because it was the war years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was difficult to obtain, and I must say, it was difficult to obtain for the Gentile population as well as for the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was much more difficult for the Jewish population because we were not permitted to go out to a farm and buy food, so we had to buy it locally, which made it more expensive and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But, and of course, there was a shortage of food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything was rationed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So some of the food had to be secured on the black market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there always was a black market in those days where you could secure food, but at a price.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the rules were-- by the time we got to Gorlice, there was really not a ghetto that was a closed-in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was sort of a ghetto whereby-- a designated area was for Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Jews had to stay in that area, although there was no wall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no fence.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had to wear our arm bands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when a Jew was-- dared to cross over outside the designated area-- which was really, in effect-- it was really a ghetto, in effect-- he was severely punished.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He could have possibly even been shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But to the best of my knowledge, I don't think that any of the Jewish population ever wandered outside that area.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If they did, they took off their arm bands or they went-- they had to have outside contacts that helped them, one way or another.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
